title: Ep. 55 "F**kboys" ft. B. Simone
description:
Comedian B. Simone is just trying to make it in a world full of fuckboys and Instagram models. You probably thought the viral f**kboy video was a skit, she tells us what really happened, how she's never reached "The Big O", and why her guy friends say she's still single. Oh, she also thinks Drake is the new Michael Jackson. Do we agree? Take a listen. You've been asking to see us and our beautiful faces so this full episode is also available on YOUTUBE!!!
